<item>
            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-2029] Leader.LearnerCnxAcceptor should handle exceptions in run()</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-2029</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Leader.LearnerCnxAcceptor swallows exceptions and shuts itself down. It should instead crash the Leader.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
