&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/zookeeper/blob/trunk/src/java/main/org/apache/zookeeper/server/quorum/Leader.java#L378&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/zookeeper/blob/trunk/src/java/main/org/apache/zookeeper/server/quorum/Leader.java#L378&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Is it a legacy code?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
